"M - Light bodied, too light. Its fantastic, but I had a few sips. Paused, went back to resume the review and its seriously almost watery. On the bright side, ridiculously easy to put down, still leaves behind a thick feel on the tongue, oddly enough. Ideal carbonation. Overall a fast/easy drinker."
